# NeuroPlay Backend Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env in your backend repository

# Supabase Configuration
# Get these from: Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key-here

# ⚠️ IMPORTANT SECURITY NOTES:
# 1. NEVER commit the .env file to git!
# 2. Add .env to your .gitignore
# 3. The service_role key has full database access - keep it secret!
# 4. For production: Set these as environment variables in Deno Deploy

# For local development:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Replace the placeholder values with your actual Supabase credentials
# 3. Run: deno run --allow-net --allow-env main.tsx

# For Deno Deploy:
# 1. Don't upload .env file
# 2. Set these as environment variables in the Deno Deploy dashboard
# 3. Project Settings → Environment Variables → Add Variable
